#: ../../manual/compositing/types/distort/scale.rst:42
msgid ""
"Stretch distorts the image so that it fits into the render size. Fit scales "
"the image until the bigger axis \"fits\" into the render size. Crop cuts the "
"image so that it is the same aspect ratio as the render size."
